PLACEHOLDER — Replace this file with your actual hero-video.mp4

Instructions:
1. Download a free medical/hair treatment video from:
   https://www.pexels.com/search/videos/hair%20treatment/
2. Rename it to: hero-video.mp4
3. Upload it to GitHub at: /public/videos/hero-video.mp4
4. The website will automatically use it as the hero background video.

Recommended specs:
- Resolution: 1920×1080 (Full HD)
- Duration: 10-30 seconds (looped)
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Size: under 10MB for fast loading
